svg.title: Lyra
svg.text: LYRA (Leverage Yield Risk Analytics) is our proprietary AI system developed byour research team to access public data to help manage risks involved inleverage farming.
The 3 Key indicators we work on before deploying any funds into any DefiProtocols are Smart Contract Integrity, On Chain Data and Social Sentiments.
Smart Contract Integrity - By incorporating smart contract audits, we canprevent “rug pull’s” and exploits
On Chain Data - to ensure that protocol funds fairly distributed and there isno potential pump and dump activities by whales or protocol owners.
Social Sentiments - helps keep track on the pulse of the markets. Our AIsentiment and machine learning technology, we can cleverly detect change inmarket sentiments
